  "text": "To broaden the basis for molecular characterization and classification of the phytoplasmas and to explore other targets for detection of these pathogens by PCR amplification, we examined the gene encoding the elongation factor Tu. This gene proved to be suitable for these purposes in work with culturable mollicutes and other [CITATION_1] .",
